view.name: NY Municipalities and County FIPS codes
view.attribution: NYS Office of Information Technology Services
view.description: The dataset contains a hierarchal listing of New York State counties, cities, towns, and villages, as well as official locality websites

columns.name: City Name
columns.description: City name, if applicable; blank if Type is not ‘City’ or 'Borough/County'.

columns.name: Town Name
columns.description: Town name, if applicable; blank if Type is not ‘Town’.

columns.name: Village Name
columns.description: Village name, if applicable; blank if Type is not ‘Village’.

columns.name: Municipality
columns.description: Name of municipality, if applicable; blank if Type is ‘County’.

columns.name: County FIPS
columns.description: 5-digit county FIPS code (concatenated state FIPS and county codes) that uniquely identifies each county in each state.

Disclaimers.Limitations: Websites are current as of last update.   Where a website did not exist, the data element for the website is blank.
